        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Volunteer Driver Tax Appreciation Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill increases the mileage rate for the charitable use of an automobile (14 cents per mile) to the standard business mileage rate (58.5 cents per mile in 2022).</p>]]>
        </text>
